      <title>亚马逊将关闭魁北克仓库，裁员 1900 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/amazon-to-close-all-warehouses-in-quebec</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司将关闭加拿大法语区魁北克省的所有仓库并裁员。这一决定是在其中一个仓库的工人成立工会不到一年后做出的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/amazon-to-close-all-warehouses-in-quebec</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 15:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者抢购 20 年期债券，推高美国收益率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/treasuries-stabilize-as-traders-weigh-trump-s-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府债券回吐了过去一周的部分大幅涨幅，最近受到押注美国总统唐纳德·特朗普将对关税采取更慎重态度的刺激，因为 20 年期债券的拍卖使美国国债供应重新成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/treasuries-stabilize-as-traders-weigh-trump-s-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 09:17:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
